game.name: Ariel Fashion Dress Store
game.description:
The popular Disney princess Ariel always has something different to share with you.  And, the fun becomes double when Anna and Elsa together come into the picture. Ariel is an owner of a popular fashion store where two other renowned princesses like Anna and Elsa generally visit to shop for their desired dresses and other needful accessories like handbags and trendy shoes. You will join this brand new dressing game as a new employee of the store in Ariel Fashion Dress Store.
Your primary objective in this brand new dressing game for girls is to help Ariel to attend her all customers. This job is not going to be easy at all since customers keep coming one by one. Make sure that the princess does not miss any product query raised by her customers. Some customers ask you for a beautiful gown or sandle, while others might have a need of purchasing a matching handbag. Try to complete all their orders timely!
Do not bother they will clear the payment for all the products they purchase through cards on the spot. Select the item and give it to the hands of Ariel who will handover it to her customers in this one of the best html5 princess games for kids! It will be amazing to play with different colored dresses and other accessories. Check out more dress up games for girls and develop your fashion sense in a friendly environment!
